wikipedia_page.main: George Kenneth Robert McKinley (born 3 November 1993) is a cricketer from Larne, Northern Ireland, who has played at Larne Grammar School, Larne town and Ballymena, then at first-class level for Loughborough MCC University. He debuted for them during the 2015 English season, having earlier played for the Ireland national under-19 side.He made his List A debut for Northern Knights in the 2017 Inter-Provincial Cup on 29 May 2017. He made his Twenty20 debut for Northern Knights in the 2017 Inter-Provincial Trophy on 16 June 2017.
